{"tid":659121,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個你最鍾意既遊戲角色","createTime":"2018-05-09T14:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T15:55:16.000Z","uid":61889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0be1c9fdd7b7b30137613a262a3cc2c95524ba","tid":659121,"uid":61889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"Big Boss                                                                                                  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/211923_229f5295de3f8f6b528b991858dbcff6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F211923_229f5295de3f8f6b528b991858dbcff6.jpg&h=173a32c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然唔係MGS系列既第一主角, 但Big Boss絕對係支撐住整個故事既靈魂人物<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/213531_9080eb3311100bc35b362ed45dbe1421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F213531_9080eb3311100bc35b362ed45dbe1421.jpg&h=3397b73e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由畫質仲係起哂格既MG2擔當最終大佬, 當時既Big Boss只係玩家眼中既恐怖分子。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/213543_11c22433fa74ea22d5fd1e10b173b87a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F213543_11c22433fa74ea22d5fd1e10b173b87a.gif&h=8a970b98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到PS2年代既MGS3擔正主角, 講述Big Boss既誕生同埋背後手刃恩師拯救世界既故事, 可恨之人必有可憐之處。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/221252_07fa9ee7e9256197cfed1fac0fe6eaf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F221252_07fa9ee7e9256197cfed1fac0fe6eaf7.jpg&h=e4ad79c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到後來PSP同PS4上既MGSPW同MGSV講述Big Boss既崛起同如何出賣世界成為MG2裏既最終大佬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/214237_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F214237_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=c8d83d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPS3年代既MGS4係整個故事既終點, Big Boss已經係個面上只有滄桑, 心中只有孤獨既老人, 昔日並肩作戰既所有戰友已經不在人世, 一生奉獻比戰爭只為追隨恩師遺願既傳奇士兵到最後一無所有, 仲將世界引向滅亡, Big Boss終於意識到所謂既傳奇到頭來都只不過係一個老糊塗, 曾經作為敵人既主角Solid Snake為他點起雪茄, 歷經沙場既Big Boss流下了男兒淚, 臨死前終於察覺到原來辛福就係咁簡單。&quot;This is good, isn't it?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &quot;<br />\n<br />\n呢個角色可以話係陪伴住我成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9249478ec082936f682270cc24285ec1f08224f5","tid":659121,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"寵物小精靈 - 渡<br />\n<br />\n拳皇 - K', Kula <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e388706096c4b224661fe72a584e7ebb6fb185","tid":659121,"uid":103339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:21:50.000Z","msg":"冰火佬，邪鬼<br />\n光頭和尚：「喝！」"},{"pid":"408eb8518c67304bcd1785c83fde3eb091cef928","tid":659121,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"Manhunt入面個piggsy"},{"pid":"9f4c1949cf573a4a69fc6fd9741f460961e3bf92","tid":659121,"uid":61889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83e388706096c4b224661fe72a584e7ebb6fb185","tid":659121,"uid":103339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:21:50.000Z","msg":"冰火佬，邪鬼<br />\n光頭和尚：「喝！」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"諗返以前同FD玩LF2既時光，依加已經各散東西<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1235b97c0cc31b48400c422546af41ad1b01a43","tid":659121,"uid":179862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"刺客信條2 Ezio<br />\n生化危機4 leo<br />\n真三國無雙 歷代虎牢關既呂布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}